findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function excludeMultipleAccountsFromFees() uses a loop to exclude multiple accounts from fees and may abort with an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long list of addresses.

findings.title: Dividend tracker may be changed
findings.description: The logic of setBalance and other functions could be another and not audited.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters and perform sensitive actions without proper access control.
